Can be performed up to three times in a row, but it takes 24 hours to recover 1 use.

name: River's Heart
description:
Attempts to discover a blue Pandaria gem recipe of superior quality.  If you have learned all blue gem recipes, you may discover a recipe for another color gem.

You can only perform one Pandaria research per day.
